@node Formatting Automake Include Sections
@chapter Formatting Automake Include Sections

@cindex Automake include section
@cindex include section, Automake
@noindent
A sequence of zero or more lines of text that is immediately preceded by
a line containing exactly
``@w{@t{## begin_includes}}'',
that is immediately followed by a line containing exactly
``@w{@t{## end_includes}}'',
and that does not contain any lines beginning with
``@w{@t{## begin_}}''
or
``@w{@t{## end_}}''
is called an
@i{Automake include section}@.
